OL,7,FThe structure took eight years to
OL,8,Fconstruct, at a cost of #535 million `
OL,9,F#2.4 billion in today's money ` and
OL,10,Fconsists of 10 steel gates, with the
OL,11,Fmain gates each as wide as the opening
OL,12,Fof Tower Bridge, weighing 3,300
OL,13,Ftonnes, and as high as a five storey
OL,14,Fbuilding when raised.
