OL,3,CLondon's future flood defences plans
OL,4,Cas 'sleeping giant' Thames Barrier
OL,5,Cturns 40
OL,7,FSince its construction, it has been
OL,8,Fclosed 221 times to prevent flooding
OL,9,Fof the capital, working with other
OL,10,Fflood defences along the Thames to
OL,11,Fprotect 1.42 million people,
OL,12,Fresidential property worth #321
OL,13,Fbillion, hundreds of schools,
OL,14,Fhospitals, railway and train stations,
OL,15,Fand four World Heritage sites.
