OL,3,CLondon's future flood defences plans
OL,4,Cas 'sleeping giant' Thames Barrier
OL,5,Cturns 40
OL,7,FWithout the barrier, officials said
OL,8,Fstorm surges and frequent tidal
OL,9,Fflooding of the Thames would submerge
OL,10,Fbuildings along the river ` with only
OL,11,Fthe City of London itself standing on
OL,12,Fhigh ground ` risking lives and
OL,13,Flivelihoods and causing huge amounts
OL,14,Fof damage.
