OL,3,CLondon's future flood defences plans
OL,4,Cas 'sleeping giant' Thames Barrier
OL,5,Cturns 40
OL,7,FThese include raising the flood walls
OL,8,Fand defences that line the Thames
OL,9,Fdownriver of the barrier by half a
OL,10,Fmetre by 2040, and then by the same
OL,11,Famount by 2050, to the west, through
OL,12,Fcentral London.
OL,14,FAnd a decision will need to be made by
OL,15,F2040 on what to do with the barrier
OL,16,Fitself, with options including
OL,17,Fupgrading the existing barrier by
OL,18,F2070, so that the gates are not
OL,19,Fovertopped by rising seas and storm
OL,20,Fsurges, or installing a series of
OL,21,Fflood storage "reservoirs" downstream.
