OL,7,FMr Batchelor said: "Having witnessed
OL,8,Fand worked on the Thames Barrier's
OL,9,Fopening, I am immensely proud of the
OL,10,Fprotection it has provided London for
OL,11,Fthe past 40 years and will continue to
OL,12,Fprovide for years to come.
OL,14,F"Its reliability and effectiveness
OL,15,Fdemonstrate the sophistication of its
OL,16,Fdesign by a very talented group of
OL,17,Fengineers and the continued
OL,18,Fmaintenance and operation carried out
OL,19,Fby the Barrier team."
