OL,7,FHe said of the barrier: "It's like the
OL,8,Fsleeping giant, it rolls into action,
OL,9,Fit wakes up when that is needed.
OL,11,F"We have to maintain the giant in the
OL,12,Fbackground all the time," he added,
OL,13,Fpaying tribute to his team, who have a
OL,14,Frolling programme of proactive
OL,15,Fmaintenance, and routine closures, to
OL,16,Fkeep the barrier working.
