OL,7,FWhile the barrier has met the
OL,8,Fchallenge it was designed for `
OL,9,Fincluding rising sea levels factored
OL,10,Fin before climate change was part of
OL,11,Fthe conversation ` the winter of 2013/
OL,12,F2014 was extremely difficult.
OL,14,FStorms and weeks of heavy rain
OL,15,Fbringing high river flows down the
OL,16,FThames meant the barrier was closed 50
OL,17,Ftimes in 13 weeks, including 20
OL,18,Fclosures on consecutive high tides.
