OL,4,Cas 'sleeping giant' Thames Barrier
OL,5,Cturns 40
OL,7,FIf that intense use were to be
OL,8,Freplicated more frequently, it would
OL,9,Fnot leave time for the maintenance the
OL,10,Fbarrier needs to ensure it works when
OL,11,Frequired.
OL,13,FSo under the Thames Estuary 2100 plan
OL,14,Fby the Environment Agency and
OL,15,Fpartners, the walls and defences that
OL,16,Fline the Thames will be raised by half
OL,17,Fa metre over the coming decades, which
OL,18,Fwill allow the barrier to continue
OL,19,Fworking for as long as possible.
