OL,7,FMr Batchelor added that despite the
OL,8,Fsuccess in protecting London over the
OL,9,Fpast 40 years, the Environment Agency
OL,10,F"will not rest on our laurels given
OL,11,Fthe threat of rising sea levels", and
OL,12,Fwould work with partners to review and
OL,13,Fdecide on the right option for a new
OL,14,Fbarrier by 2040.
